title: Native ferns: Fronds with benefits
text:
Photo: Doreen Wynja, Doreen Wynja For Monrovia Polystichum munitum (Western Sword fern). Polystichum munitum (Western Sword fern).
Many gardeners have discovered the benefits of planting California natives, but it may surprise some that the world of ferns also offers a diverse collection of hardy natives. There are many looks from which to choose: Polystichum munitum (Western Sword fern). Polystichum munitum (Western Sword fern).
